Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.63,0:22:02.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}让迷茫一笑而过吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.93,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}不偏移的弹道
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.93,0:22:05.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}只因我才是赢家
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.43,0:22:07.22,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}这颗出膛的子弹
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.68,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}冲破枷锁
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.14,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}坚定梦想 不弃承诺
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.14,0:22:14.10,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}永不放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.60,0:22:15.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}不放弃 不放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.40,0:22:18.07,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}我已势不可当
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.07,0:22:19.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}这是我的致命一击
